text: Yi Murphey is an electrical engineer at the University of Michigan, Dearborn. She was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2014 for her contributions to optimal energy control in hybrid electric vehicles. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:21st-century American engineers Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:University of Michigan alumni
